    <item>
      <title>@labiennale Architettura Venezia 2025, a little throwback. Together with @richip...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DVMQDGqDYgn/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DVMQDGqDYgn/"><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/641428651_18569491492025576_5916544754996330963_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s640x640_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=106&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg0MDUxNTE2NDI5MDc3OTE3NTE4NTY5NDkxNDg5MDI1NTc2.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjk4MHgxNzQwLnNkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=9RrqUic7cY8Q7kNvwGSnFvD&amp;_nc_oc=Adqutyc4-qqwi-zfcd2XE_Q5CblEbDJArV1yRhHbbn018BVC94hHixmbs615f-TVf4s&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=uITLt7fUNQqptdJ3DG1jyA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwC6Yf810MlwIMwzP-lmGCrBc2z9QiwqShO9HKdVQOLFA&amp;oe=69CA3A2C" alt="Video-thumbnail fra @richipetrini" /></a></p><p><strong>🎬 Video</strong></p><p><strong>@richipetrini</strong></p><p>@labiennale Architettura Venezia 2025, a little throwback.<br/>
<br/>
Together with @richipetrini, we worked on the installation Unpredictable Atmosphere as a multichannel web interactive space, where strips of data on outliers — hurricanes that deviate from the statistical median pattern — were excluded from contemporary AI climate models. We unfolded them in space to question this growing tendency of synthetic systems to ignore extreme events, collapsing into an infinite series of modeling practices.<br/>
<br/>
Thanks to audio designer @lero____ , who worked with recordings from data centers, satellites, and transmission frequencies, carefully shaping the soundscape; to @chiararebolino for the graphics and the direction of the visual storytelling within the exhibition table; and to @alessia.rapetti for the care in drawing and designing the table itself.<br/>
<br/>
Behind the scenes, a big thanks to @chxdahmen for his support with the fluid dynamics simulation, and to @joppemassant who, like a wizard, made possible all the AI modeling of storms collected in the full dataset streamed in the space.<br/>
<br/>
Special thanks to @mt.crm for his thoughtful video report and editing of this installation video.<br/>
<br/>
And again, a unique thanks to @richipetrini , who designed this installation with me and coded a beautifully complex and branched web space where all the information has been unfolding over the past year.<br/>
<br/>
&lt;3 Looking forward to letting this web space travel beyond the internet again. &lt;3<br/>
<br/>
🌪️📡</p><p><a href="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t16/f2/m69/AQPhlfgkfJbB5mmQfObvkt3VYRVm-uy4knfgCYJOciYzOSWbU1kAtRWDrcudyi9nyihSotdyh87eAW8V58fcwKcV.mp4?strext=1&amp;_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_sid=5e9851&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_ohc=l9xHSQp2WiQQ7kNvwHOuW4O&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6Inhwdl9wcm9ncmVzc2l2ZS5JTlNUQUdSQU0uQ0xJUFMuQzMuNzIwLmRhc2hfYmFzZWxpbmVfMV92MSIsInhwdl9hc3NldF9pZCI6MTg1Njk0OTAxNzgwMjU1NzYsImFzc2V0X2FnZV9kYXlzIjoyOCwidmlfdXNlY2FzZV9pZCI6MTAwOTksImR1cmF0aW9uX3MiOjUwLCJ1cmxnZW5fc291cmNlIjoid3d3In0%3D&amp;ccb=17-1&amp;vs=6c825c8a54e641d6&amp;_nc_&amp;_nc_gid=uITLt7fUNQqptdJ3DG1jyA&amp;_nc_zt=28&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfxG1-14fbvk6t6Pml1y8OOFPkYjP82NKfB2D4HA6KeVHA&amp;oe=69CA1504">▶️ Åbn video direkte</a> · <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DVMQDGqDYgn/">se på Instagram</a></p>]]></description>
